🤩 <GIVEAWAY> Want to join @xixilimofficial and our trainers in our Private Online Build & Tone Workout Group Class this Sunday, 7 Jun 4PM? We are giving away FREE entries to this private online class with XIXI to thank you guys for helping us reach 500 followers!
-
All you have to do is to:
1) Follow @fitlucsg on IG.
2) Like & Comment on this IG Post what your fitness goals are.
3) Tag 3-5 friends so they can join too!
Share the love! ❤💪
-
Giveaway closes this Friday, 5 Jun 11.59PM SGT. We will contact you via IG DM the class details and how to get the zoom link for the class.
